title: Hokies fall at 68-55 to No. 20 Notre Dame - VT hokiesports.com
content: Hokies fall at 68-55 to No. 20 Notre Dame  VT hokiesports.com
description: NOTRE DAME, IN --The Virginia Tech women's basketball team got a 26-point showing from the bench, but fell 68-55 to the No. 20 Notre Dame Fighting Irish on the road Thursday.
